ivardefs.name: action
ivardefs.desc: Indicator for type of action performed during the event that generated the audit.

ivardefs.name: agent_
ivardefs.desc: An actor taking an active role in the event or activity that is logged.

ivardefs.name: entity_
ivardefs.desc: Specific instances of data or objects that have been accessed.

ivardefs.name: outcome
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether the event succeeded or failed.

ivardefs.name: outcomeDesc
ivardefs.desc: A free text description of the outcome of the event.

ivardefs.name: purposeOfEvent_
ivardefs.desc: The purposeOfUse (reason) that was used during the event being recorded.

ivardefs.name: recorded
ivardefs.desc: The time when the event occurred on the source.

ivardefs.name: source
ivardefs.desc: The system that is reporting the event.

ivardefs.name: subtype_
ivardefs.desc: Identifier for the category of event.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Identifier for a family of the event.  For example, a menu item, program, rule, policy, function code, application name or URL. It identifies the performed function.
